reviewText: Very few videos cover total information for beginners, the size of the blank, initial speeds and changes to speeds as the project progresses and the various tools, not just jumping on the skew which is a harder tool to master in the beginning. They did 4 out of 5 because they did not fully provide all the details but the video is well worth the time and investment. I would recommend without question.
A real prize, learned more than I expected.  It's my go to teaching tool for all new turners.
